{"name":"Sucker Punch","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>The character doesn't know the meaning of the words \"fair fight.\" If he succeeds in a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Test]{Test} against an adjacent opponent, the character receives a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Free Attacks]{free attack}. This attack does not incur a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Multi-Actions]{multi-action penalty}.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Slipstream Player's Guide</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, First Strike, Agility d6+, Fighting d8+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_ld1dvwzp8en","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"5r7URjsODRUGeg1n"}
{"name":"Reactive Shifting","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Some shifters can activate their abilities as a reflex. Reactive Shifting allows them to begin shifting as a free action even when it's not their turn.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Savage Eberron</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Shifter (any), Quick"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_lb6h1pgtb7c","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Racial Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"66Zmuq49h0ORFXKq"}
{"name":"Lunge","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>A lunge allows a swordsman to extend the reach of his weapon. The character gains +1 @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Reach]{Reach} to his weapon. He may not use this Edge with @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-edges.First Strike]{First Strike}, @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Frenzy]{Frenzy}, or @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Sweep]{Sweep}.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Lankhmar, City of Thieves</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Fighting d8+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_ld1dvwzp8en","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"6ZMNpIAbSRZS2zKz"}
{"name":"Improved Strong Caster","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>The mage is adept at channeling raw magical essence.</p>\n<p>A mage with this Edge reduces the initial Casting Modifier of all spells by 2, to a minimum of zero. For instance, a spell with a Casting Modifier of &minus;2 only inflicts a &minus;1 penalty to this mage.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Heroic, Strong Caster"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_m4fbu1ptbuc","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Power Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"6i8YEYA8yozC3V0e"}
{"name":"Healing Factor","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>After the shifter's current period of shifting ends, she may immediately make a free @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Soak Rolls]{Soak} roll to remove any @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Soak Rolls]{Wounds} taken while shifted.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Savage Eberron</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Shifter (any), Vigor d8+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_lb6h1pgtb7c","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Racial Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"77iD4oQqy4TNXUBD"}
{"name":"Disciple of Onatar","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":""}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_wc10m6m9sz","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Disciple Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"7JV9SmgyD6HizVOX"}
{"name":"Blind Fighting","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Blind fighters have trained long and hard to fight with out being able to see, using smell, sound, disturbances in the surrounding air, etc. You character is able to halves any penalties for @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Illumination]{Illumination}.</p>\n<p>Note this edge does not allow you to see in the dark only to fight at a reduced penalty when you vision is impaired.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Legnds of Steel</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Agility d8+, Notice d8+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_ld1dvwzp8en","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"7KQlEnIeajJ2IWfe"}
{"name":"Artificer","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Artificers with this Edge have the ability to make minor artifacts. Runes or embedded dragonshards are the most common \"trapping\" of this Edge, but such details are left to the individual artificer.</p>\n<p>On taking this @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-lore.Edges]{Edge}, the hero may craft (or modify) an item that adds +1 to the one trait roll, increases the damage of a weapon by +1, or increases the bonus of armor by +1. No activation roll is required.</p>\n<p>Only items that were crafted with a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Trait Rolls]{raise} have enough quality to be magically imbued with this kind of power.</p>\n<p>Assuming the artificer is always \"fiddling\" with devices (not locked in a dungeon, for example), has adequate tools, and uses 250 galfiars worth of Eberron Dragonshards, he may make an @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Arcane Backgrounds]{arcane skill} roll at &ndash;4 at the end of any session in which he advances. If successful, he adds another +1 to any item of his choice.</p>\n<p>This could be his own blade, the cloak of another, or any other item of his choice. The item now adds that bonus to the user's relevant trait or damage roll, or armor rating. No item may have more than a +3 total bonuses (such devices are relics and outside the scope of this ability). The bonuses need not apply to the same trait.</p>\n<p><strong>Stacking:</strong> Bonuses from items don't stack, so a sword +3 (Fighting) wielded by someone with gauntlets +3 (Fighting) gets only the highest of the two.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Fantasy Gear Toolkit</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (Dragonmark of Making, Magecraft, Magic, or Miracles), Arcana d10+, arcane skill d8+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_m4fbu1ptbuc","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Power Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"7jkJDw5RrpLQPyzS"}
{"name":"Disciple of Dol Arrah","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Dol Arrah]{Dol Arrah} disciples treat his character @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Advancement]{Rank} as being one higher for the purposes of taking Combat Edges. He must meet all other requirements as normal.</p>\n<p>In addition, they gain +2 to all @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Notice]{Notice} rolls to detect hidden objects or creatures, including those under an <em>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Invisibilty]{Invisibilty} </em>spell. Against foes cloaked in such a manner, they halve penalties to hit them (once they have detected them).</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (Divine Magic), Faith d8+, Fighting d8+, Notice d6+, follower of Dol Dorn"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_wc10m6m9sz","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Disciple Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"8c9c22UIzBLMWEok"}
