{"name":"Bladedancer","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Bladedancers are elite elven warriors, this Edge is their trademark combat maneuver. Despite the name, they may use weapons.</p>\n<p>When used, an elf spins and dances about, attacking every opponent in his path like a deadly cyclone. On the tabletop, the character makes a running roll and must move that many inches. He may not double back.</p>\n<p>Every target adjacent to the fighter's path, starting with his initial position, is attacked at &minus;2. One small downside to this Edge is that every adjacent target must be attacked&mdash;whether friend or foe. Individual targets may only be attacked once while using this Edge.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Hellfrost Player Guide</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Elf, Agility d8+, Fighting d8+, Two-Fisted"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_lb6h1pgtb7c","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Racial Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"C1G3m1WpsJ1zvWqR"}
