{"name":"Improved Scamper","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>The halfling can move so quickly as to cause multiple opponents to interfere with each other's attacks. Opponents get no @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Ganging Up]{Ganging Up} bonus against the halfling.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Fantasy Companion</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Scamper"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_lb6h1pgtb7c","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Racial Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"KUNZgFYaB40jP3TZ"}
{"name":"Arcane Background (Dragonmark)","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Arcane Background (Dragonmark)]{Arcane Background (Dragonmark)}</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Dragonmarked Race, Spirit d8+, Dragonmarked Focus d4+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_xoh0o6iqdor","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Background Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"LjI5m8tCLcx24O6f"}
{"name":"Wind Sense","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>The character has an almost supernatural knowledge of air and wind. He can sense changes in the weather and wind direction long before they actually happen.</p>\n<p>If the character is piloting a ship he gains +1 to @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Boating]{Boating} or @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Piloting]{Piloting} rolls during Contact, using his knowledge of the winds to outrun and catch prey.</p>\n<p>In addition, the character may draw two cards during a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Chases and Vehicles]{Chase} each round during a storm and keeps the best as long as the Captain heeds his warnings. If the character has the @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Storm Chaser]{Storm Chaser} Edge as well he draws three cards.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: 50 Fathoms</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Smarts d8+, Boating or Piloting d8+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_z6bv3ii8tjh","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Weird Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"NWrWXDfJSNbkefhH"}
{"name":"Primal Fury","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Some half-orcs or orcs have an animal rage inside them they can trigger consciously. A half-orc or orc with Prinal Fury may spend a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Bennies]{Benny} to activate his @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Berserk]{Berserk} Edge.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Fantasy Companion</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Half-orc or Orc, Berserk"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_lb6h1pgtb7c","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Racial Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"OFuPTozzFFZXXvAE"}
