{"name":"Death before Dishonor","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>This Edge is used only for @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Mass Battles]{Mass Battles}. The character has led his army to many victories, and the men have come to accept retreat as a stain on their honor.</p>\n<p>The character gains +2 to @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Spirit} rolls when rolling for Morale in a Mass Battle.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Hellfrost Player Guide</strong></em></p>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Hold the Line, Spirit d8+, Battle d8+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_vbsguwz7lo","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Leadership Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"VaBSaUf7dZm5qEsL"}
{"name":"Symbiont Mastery","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>The adventurer has stronger control over attached symbionts and benefits from increased vitality from the attached symbionts. She gains a +2 bonus to @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Spirit} rolls during any battle of wills between her and the symbiont (see Intelligent Relics in Fantasy Companion). While at least one symbiont is attached, the adventurer also gains a free reroll on @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Soak Rolls]{Soak} rolls.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Savage Eberron</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Spirit d6+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_z6bv3ii8tjh","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Weird Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"YhY6qiUPE7otErhV"}
